{"tid":1653344,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"發唔發覺班割蔗撚好鍾意將自己接受唔到既行為屈係鬼做","createTime":"2019-10-14T04:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T05:12:31.000Z","uid":57076,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7be6605e2a9828254adecbae91df886385edb33c","tid":1653344,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxpVWeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxpVWeQ.png&h=3d542f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n觀塘站割頸被捕人士<br />\n<br />\n唔知連登係真心定假膠，有人居然話係中共特務做<br />\n<br />\n平時就話核彈都唔割，又叫人出手，點知有人出手，就話係中共特務做，又話班狗既自己人做<br />\n<br />\n講之前用下腦得唔得<br />\n<br />\n如果中共特務做，隻狗會唔會有命留低，仲要有人被捕？ 班狗會想殺自己人？<br />\n<br />\n如果係假膠，想嫁禍比中共特務做，都係唔會改變被捕受審結果<br />\n你地咁做只係令到有真心既人相信，而被捕人士孤立無援，正如幾年前被捕手中一樣被割<br />\n<br />\n最後一句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宇宙大爆炸都唔割</span></span>"},{"pid":"0954bd4f04a0f3b347829b3c143fe5d75b6c2bdf","tid":1653344,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"不願面對，繼續負評啦"},{"pid":"4deb77f6d525fbdc6c88196d3478c140295e71cf","tid":1653344,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"ef9184e011b233d4da7e9eb5c1489df6d3a8cef3","tid":1653344,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"反宣傳同唔割根本無衝突<br />\n對面都成日做反宣傳洗白啦<br />\n唔好指責做反宣傳既同路人<br />\n唔好互相指責<br />\n不分化"},{"pid":"26d51bab128c9028f792d1d3bf3e25005f8f5bfb","tid":1653344,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effac08d7572396da1c0fd1fcb6c45c9f6f6812b","tid":1653344,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"push"}]}